Emily O'Brien https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_O%27Brien 0 Emily Roya O'Brien (born May 28, 1985) is an English-born, half Persian actress. She is known for her roles as Jana Hawkes Fisher on The Young and the Restless, Julia in Pernicious and the voice of Y'Shtola in Final Fantasy XIV: A Realm Reborn. She has also portrayed Gamora in Guardians of the Galaxy: The Telltale Series Special Agent Iman Avesta in Batman: The Enemy Within and Ruth in the upcoming animated film Dagon Troll World Chronicles .
